text: Arthrosaura testigensis is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Venezuelan grasslands. ==References== Category:Arthrosaura Category:Reptiles described in 1999 Category:Reptiles of Venezuela Category:Endemic fauna of Venezuela Category:Taxa named by Stefan Jan Filip Gorzula Category:Taxa named by Josefa Celsa Señaris
title: Arthrosaura testigensis
